01:00:07,017 --> 01:00:07,717
Get back! Get back!

850
01:00:07,717 --> 01:00:08,717
Pack your dummy, pack your bomb, bomb!

851
01:00:08,717 --> 01:00:09,817
Let's just crash!

852
01:00:09,817 --> 01:00:11,617
So get out of the way!

853
01:00:11,617 --> 01:00:16,117
くだらねぇキャラばかりに
All these useless characters

854
01:00:16,117 --> 01:00:17,017
笑い
laughing

855
01:00:17,017 --> 01:00:17,917
殺して
Kill them

856
01:00:17,917 --> 01:00:19,617
美しく
beautifully

857
01:00:19,617 --> 01:00:22,617
歪な世界で
In this warped world

858
01:00:22,617 --> 01:00:25,017
ほら ぶつけ重ねた光
See, the clashing, overlapping light

859
01:00:25,017 --> 01:00:28,817
脈打つ鼓動 誰も止められない
Pulsing heartbeat that no one can stop

860
01:00:28,817 --> 01:00:31,617
言葉を紡いで
Spinning words

861
01:00:31,817 --> 01:00:33,617
We fall

862
01:00:33,617 --> 01:00:35,617
we break

863
01:00:35,617 --> 01:00:39,017
we drown in fire

864
01:00:39,017 --> 01:00:42,617
lost inside this dark desire

865
01:00:43,417 --> 01:00:46,817
Sorrow 孵化する未来の mercy
Sorrow, mercy of the hatching future

866
01:00:46,817 --> 01:00:49,817
Mercy! Mercy!

867
01:00:49,817 --> 01:00:53,617
微動だにしない異彩の愛に
In this unbudging, eccentric love

868
01:00:53,617 --> 01:00:55,617
偽物だって
Saying I'm a fake

869
01:00:55,617 --> 01:00:57,817
Tell me what I'm to not say

870
01:00:57,817 --> 01:00:59,217
What's your problem?

871
01:00:59,217 --> 01:01:01,217
夜を一人
All alone in the night

872
01:01:01,217 --> 01:01:03,617
あたしが迷う
I get lost

873
01:01:04,117 --> 01:01:06,417
When thunder crashes down

874
01:01:06,417 --> 01:01:11,617
When the world caves under my pressure

875
01:01:11,617 --> 01:01:13,617
There'll be no one to save

876
01:01:13,617 --> 01:01:17,417
巡る巡る 運命に抗って
Resisting the revolving, revolving fate

877
01:01:17,417 --> 01:01:21,117
出会いを 迷いを 酔わせた
Making encounters and hesitation drunk

878
01:01:21,117 --> 01:01:24,617
The strangers I followed with stars in...

879
01:01:25,117 --> 01:01:27,617
So I keep on waiting

880
01:01:27,617 --> 01:01:29,617
Wanting...

881
01:01:29,617 --> 01:01:32,117
Faking you're someone you're not

882
01:01:32,117 --> 01:01:34,617
Reaching... Longing...

883
01:01:34,817 --> 01:01:38,017
No, I can't be someone else

884
01:01:38,017 --> 01:01:42,317
Despite it all, my mind has become my hell

885
01:01:42,317 --> 01:01:46,817
With no escape, we're hoping in the dark

886
01:01:46,817 --> 01:01:48,617
but still...

887
01:01:50,617 --> 01:01:53,617
クラクラするでしょ？
You feel dizzy, right?

888
01:01:53,617 --> 01:01:56,617
ほら、ホラ、溶けそう
See, see, about to melt

889
01:01:56,617 --> 01:01:59,617
そうでしょ？ FLASH BANG
Right? FLASH BANG

890
01:02:00,017 --> 01:02:03,017
In this moment

891
01:02:03,017 --> 01:02:06,217
Maybe eyes open wide

892
01:02:06,217 --> 01:02:09,617
Knowing if I never try

893
01:02:10,117 --> 01:02:13,117
夢を夢見る度
Every time I dream a dream

894
01:02:13,117 --> 01:02:18,117
生まれた意味を考えてしまうの
I end up thinking about the meaning of being born

895
01:02:18,117 --> 01:02:20,617
あぁ 美しい青い日々
Ah, beautiful blue days

896
01:02:21,117 --> 01:02:23,117
We fall

897
01:02:23,117 --> 01:02:25,117
we break

898
01:02:25,117 --> 01:02:28,117
we drown in fire

899
01:02:28,117 --> 01:02:32,117
lost inside this dark desire

900
01:02:32,117 --> 01:02:34,617
No love

901
01:02:34,617 --> 01:02:36,617
no faith

